(4280, 2254, 'about_us', '<h2>What is FullBottle?</h2>\r\nFullbottle is a marketing technology platform that enables advertisers to program, promote and distribute videos created by influencers. Social video has supplanted television as the preferred entertainment format amongst Millennials and Centennials.\r\n\r\nThe team at fullbottle is leading the world’s biggest brands into social video with the first platform that streamlines influencer discovery and delivers performance driven pricing.\r\n\r\nAdvertisers benefit when their story is told through authentic voices who deliver audience engagement metrics that consistently outperform industry benchmarks. Our clients include distinguished global brands such as Fox, Kraft, McDonald’s, Universal, iHeartMedia, Warner Bros., Kellogg’s, Lego, Macy’s, Hasbro, Nintendo and many more. Fullbottle is headquartered in the San Francisco Bay Area with offices in Miami, Santa Monica, New York, and Chicago.\r\n\r\nLearn more at fullbottlegroup.com.'),
