(1798, 4, '2015-01-21 18:02:18', '2015-01-21 18:02:18', '<a href="http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2015/01/15/as-pinterest-pitches-ads-brands-flock-to-pinfluencers/">‘Pinfluencers’ Are Getting Paid. Pinterest Itself, Not So Much</a>\n<div class="link_description">\n\nBrandon Berger, chief digital officer at the agency Ogilvy &amp; Mather Worldwide, says Pinterest could potentially profit from the interest in influencers by playing a role in matching brands with them. “Does the advertising on Pinterest evolve from inserting brands into the site to a marketplace for the individuals who know their audiences best?” he asked.\n\n</div>', '‘Pinfluencers’ Are Getting Paid. Pinterest Itself, Not So Much', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pinfluencers-are-getting-paid-pinterest-itself', '', '', '2015-01-21 18:02:18', '2015-01-21 18:02:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/pinfluencers-are-getting-paid-pinterest-itself/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1799, 4, '2015-01-20 17:44:13', '2015-01-20 17:44:13', '<a href="https://imgflip.com/i/gm3rd"><img title="made at imgflip.com" src="https://i.imgflip.com/gm3rd.jpg" alt="" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://www.business2community.com/social-media/6-strategies-add-social-media-marketing-plan-2015-01130207" target="_blank">Check out detailed information about these tips by reading this blog.</a>\n\n#1: Build a Community Rather Than a Number of Followers\n#2: Create Powerful Social Media Movements Across all Social Channels\n#3: Experiment with Facebook Advertisements\n#4: Host or participate in Twitter chats\n<strong>#5: Discover influencers that are specific to your industry </strong>\n#6: Share trending content\n\n<a href="http://bottlefeed.fullbottlegroup.com/post/108116181782/now-thats-music-volume-52-release-in-october" target="_blank">Working with influencers is easy, fun and effective. See the results for yourself; here’s video about a music campaign that was aiming to reach teens and young adults</a><a href="http://bottlefeed.fullbottlegroup.com/post/108116181782/now-thats-music-volume-52-release-in-october" target="_blank">.</a>', '6 Social Media Tips for Advertisers in 2015', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '6-social-media-tips-for-advertisers-in-2015', '', '', '2015-01-20 17:44:13', '2015-01-20 17:44:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/6-social-media-tips-for-advertisers-in-2015/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
